{"tid":667922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本新宿傳3500萬現金搶案      受害人、搶匪都是中國人","createTime":"2018-05-17T07:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T06:43:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"24a5d0c550be9328f344117208b97fa20f001e01","tid":667922,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"日本東京新宿鬧區今天（2日）下午，傳出一起3500萬日圓（約新台幣950萬）搶案，受害人和2名搶匪都是中國籍人士，警方正展開追查。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，受害的32歲中國籍男子表示，他替人到銀樓將金塊換成約3500萬日圓的現金，回到位在新宿的「東京留學支援中心」辦公室，卻疑似遭到2名中國籍歹徒尾隨闖入，用中文警告他「不想受傷就安靜一點！」，隨後歹徒將他用膠帶綑綁在辦公椅上，並搶走所有現金。<br />\n<br />\n受害人自行掙脫後，才跑到附近的派出所報案，目前警視廳新宿署將本案以強盜事件展開追查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2413811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2413811&d=mEyK4i52j5nGS%2BFZh4gAfozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2b43d692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2413811&h=43afb5d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2413811</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b9d17673cde337d2dd6927483bdb523e6fb39f","tid":667922,"uid":141151,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"輸出罪案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4172c4c1c10f88d58ed9d16b4702c207c6524df1","tid":667922,"uid":139456,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"佢又聽得明大陸話<br />\n兩條匪又知佢聽得明而同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c41456cb70fcb288c768d08e8354743a6ae96fd","tid":667922,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4172c4c1c10f88d58ed9d16b4702c207c6524df1","tid":667922,"uid":139456,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"佢又聽得明大陸話<br />\n兩條匪又知佢聽得